Title: Relates to adding 7-Hydroxymitragynine to the schedule of controlled substances
Summary: Adds 7-Hydroxymitragynine, including its salts, isomers and salts of isomers, as a schedule 1 controlled substance.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to adding 7-Hydroxymitragynine to the schedule of controlled substances
